<article id="post-770550" class="post-770550 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-data-and-information category-systems-and-networking issue-september-2025 section-research-highlights">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/research-highlights/">Research Highlights</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">TMO: Transparent Memory Offloading in Datacenters</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>This paper introduces TMO, Meta’s transparent memory offloading solution for heterogeneous datacenter environments.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/johannes-weiner/" title="Posts by Johannes Weiner" class="author url fn" rel="author">Johannes Weiner</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/niket-agarwal/" title="Posts by Niket Agarwal" class="author url fn" rel="author">Niket Agarwal</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/dan-schatzberg/" title="Posts by Dan Schatzberg" class="author url fn" rel="author">Dan Schatzberg</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/leon-yang/" title="Posts by Leon Yang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Leon Yang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/hao-wang/" title="Posts by Hao Wang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Hao Wang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/blaise-sanouillet/" title="Posts by Blaise Sanouillet" class="author url fn" rel="author">Blaise Sanouillet</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/bikash-sharma/" title="Posts by Bikash Sharma" class="author url fn" rel="author">Bikash Sharma</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/tejun-heo/" title="Posts by Tejun Heo" class="author url fn" rel="author">Tejun Heo</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/mayank-jain/" title="Posts by Mayank Jain" class="author url fn" rel="author">Mayank Jain</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/chunqiang-tang/" title="Posts by Chunqiang Tang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Chunqiang Tang</a>, and <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/dimitrios-skarlatos/" title="Posts by Dimitrios Skarlatos" class="author url fn" rel="author">Dimitrios Skarlatos</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2025-08-27T12:42:30-04:00">Aug 27 2025</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

			<figure class="article-header__figure">
			<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="forklift and digital containers, illustration" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg 2400w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/081425.RH-TMO-S.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>		</figure>

