</li>
<li class="ref">
<div id="B23" class="citation"><span class="label">23.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="book"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Yang</span>, <span class="given-names">J. </span></span><span class="etal">et al.</span> </span><span class="chapter-title">An empirical guide to the behavior and use of scalable persistent memory</span>. In <em><span class="source">Proceedings of the 18th USENIX Conf. on File and Storage Technologies</span></em>, <span class="publisher-name">USENIX Association</span> (Feb. <span class="year">2020)</span>, <span class="fpage">169</span>–<span class="lpage">182</span>.</span></div>
</li>
<li class="ref">
<div id="B24" class="citation"><span class="label">24.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="book"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Zheng</span>, <span class="given-names">S.</span></span>, <span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Hoseinzadeh</span>, <span class="given-names">M.</span></span>, and <span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Swanson</span>, <span class="given-names">S.</span></span> </span><span class="chapter-title">Ziggurat: A tiered file system for non-volatile main memories and disks</span>. In <em><span class="source">Proceedings of the  </span><span class="source">17th USENIX Conf. on File and Storage Technologies</span></em>, <span class="publisher-name">USENIX Association</span> (Feb. <span class="year">2019)</span>, <span class="fpage">207</span>–<span class="lpage">219</span>.</span></div>
</li>
<li class="ref">
<div id="B25" class="citation"><span class="label">25.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="other"><span class="collab">zswap;</span> <a class="ext-link" href="https://www.kernel.org/doc/html/latest/vm/zswap.html" data-jats-ext-link-type="uri">https://www.kernel.org/doc/html/latest/vm/zswap.html</a>.</span></div>
</li>
</ul>
</section>
	</ul>
</section>
